{"tid":442309,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國電視劇製作量世界第一  冀成文化輸出大國","createTime":"2017-10-20T13:15:20.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-20T23:08:31.000Z","uid":141461,"like":1,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"c3c513cf838f173166234818b6e9826efbff1393","tid":442309,"uid":141461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T13:15:20.000Z","msg":"廣電總局表示，中國在電視劇製作量世界第一；電影市場領先世界會繼續推動創新，爭取成為文化輸出大國。<br />\n<br />\n愛國主義電影《戰狼2》今年橫掃內地，總票房至今超過56億元人民幣，還代表內地出戰明年奧斯卡外語片。<br />\n<br />\n新聞出版廣電總局在十九大記者會稱，未來會繼續推動電影業改革，以打入世界市場，爭取國際話語權。<br />\n<br />\n新聞出版廣電總局副局長張宏森表示：「在創作上我們不斷開拓電影題材、體裁、類型、樣式，讓更多優秀作品和創新型作品，佔據電影市場主體。在人才培養上，我們打破傳統模式，樹立講品位、講格調、長責任的創作風氣，自覺抵制低俗、庸俗、媚俗。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img1.ahtv.cn/material/news/img/2014/09/554cc956a14d1e5d36c4953282274b02.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg1.ahtv.cn%2Fmaterial%2Fnews%2Fimg%2F2014%2F09%2F554cc956a14d1e5d36c4953282274b02.jpg&h=6ca5e242&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"04ebc37f38be44b3d5c3064710ac9619ff9e054d","tid":442309,"uid":3773,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T13:16:04.000Z","msg":"世界文化災難"},{"pid":"37abb28dc72ee567d3f021b726ea2611059f80c5","tid":442309,"uid":46644,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T13:16:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"760f1e71bc98e2f5d9bc0162f28b6d3e4f5aeb6a","tid":442309,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T13:18:35.000Z","msg":"抗日片數目世界第一<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57d84b414bb3cab4ff9202bb2c848a7159423b08","tid":442309,"uid":140737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T13:18:43.000Z","msg":"三國，司馬懿軍師都ok<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa64dd0312598db33915e4f50004bdd0eeae9e40","tid":442309,"uid":10157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T13:23:25.000Z","msg":"金仔都話北韓第一，究竟邊個先真<img src=\"/assets/f